posting_body: ['Wallace on Sunset', '6240 West Sunset Blvd.', 'Los Angeles, CA 90028', 'show contact info', '<URL>', 'Come home to happiness and let us help you find your new apartment today!', 'SPECIALS:  4 WEEKS FREE!!', 'SAVE $5530!', ' PLUS 1 FREE PARKING SPACE FOR YEAR!', 'MUST APPLY SAME DAY AS YOUR TOUR TO GET FREE PARKING SPACE!', 'Available August 4th', 'Apartment #440', '3 Bedroom/ 2 Bath', '1396sf', '$5530* on a 12 Month Lease!', 'CONTACT US TODAY TO LEARN MORE AND SCHEDULE A TOUR!', 'Finding your new apartment home has never been easier with our self-guided tours (currently limited to', 'two people per tour), 360-degree online tours, virtual tours and our quick-and-easy online application', 'process.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> to schedule a tour online.', 'THE ESSEX DIFFERENCE', '30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee', 'We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee with any leased apartment.', 'If you’re not 100% satisfied with', 'your new home, we’ll help you transfer to a comparable home within the same community or you can', 'choose to terminate your lease.*', 'On-Site Maintenance', 'From replacing a light bulb to fixing an after-hours water leak, we are here for our residents.', 'Our', 'maintenance team provides on-site support to keep your apartment and our community running', 'smoothly.', 'We’re even available 24/7 for emergency issues that might arise.', 'At Essex, we’ve got you', 'covered.', '*Pricing and Specials are Subject to Change at Any Time']
